  <name>Gydl</name>
  <summary>Download content from sites like YouTube</summary>
  <developer_name>Jannik Hauptvogel</developer_name>
  <description>
    <p>
      Gydl (Graphical youtube-dl) is a tool that enables downloading of content from
      YouTube and many other sites. It provides a minimal interface based on dialogues,
      making it quick and easy to download multimedia content.
    </p>
    <p>
      Because user needs vary, Gydl supports both audio and video downloads. If a
      selected format is not available at the source, Gydl will attempt to convert it.
    </p>
    <p>
      Gydl is based upon the popular youtube-dl program, which can be found on GitHub.
      A big thank you to the developer(s).
    </p>
  </description>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">com.github.JannikHv.Gydl.desktop</launchable>
